message:
If you want to put this in terms of your framework;

There is a significant amount of time I will need to take to ingest your framework, examine extant literature, compare to prior art, and then articulate what makes it different.

When presenting novel research and asking for people's time we need to be clear why this formalism is not just using different words to describe something that's been done to death already

-
@leo.guinan has tuned his LLM use to feel like a trick I call "anti-alchemy"

where Craft is used upon people so they can see the craft and therefore become immunized against dark magic

--
@leo.guinan 

what do we do about the time violence Good uses to forestall Evils incursions such that God's Will allows an actionable path of maximal selfhood to him become performed by the dance of all shared time together towards non-comprehension?
